{"tid":379850,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"2017 dse 中文得2想讀翻上Nursing 求指點","createTime":"2017-08-29T16:19:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T10:03:12.000Z","uid":141635,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2d13da18aacdcb8415ca35a3292ad0a491367ba6","tid":379850,"uid":141635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T16:19:16.000Z","msg":"小妹係2017 DSE 中文一個唔小心就2左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n放榜個日真係覺得人生無希望<br />\n但cc Health studies 都收左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都叫有機會上翻Nursing<br />\n但到今日聽完hs introduction 先記翻起<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nNursing council minimum requirement 3322<br />\n姐係我中文無3就一世無可能讀到Nursing<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁姐係我依家就要一邊讀Asso 一邊retake<br />\n但又真係咁唔好彩中文改制出範文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下咁多位大大 如果我考IGCSE 中文可唔可以replace 翻dse 中文個result?<br />\n定我頂硬上retake中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nretake中文dse 俾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n考IGCSE 俾個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔該晒大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c36031326ae4ae4aa7685de474cb59b739fc5618","tid":379850,"uid":5777,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T16:22:44.000Z","msg":"你讀nursing咪又係為錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55c2d44cfc93e60847be3053c2e73b3bf96868a3","tid":379850,"uid":128972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T16:25:43.000Z","msg":"走後門囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8f17acd342704b69129381213567e09242f64a7","tid":379850,"uid":7748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T16:29:41.000Z","msg":"IGCSE E or above"},{"pid":"6595b7494b77c829d731163414662498b5ddc295","tid":379850,"uid":141635,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T16:33:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你讀nursing咪又係為錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實如果要搵錢的話 我大可以去做秘書 一勞永逸 人工又高<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但個人真心鐘情於醫護行業 唔識講 但我好鐘意關於人體 睇住自己照顧既病人康復走出醫院個種幫到人既感覺<br />\n護士人工係吸引，但相對都真係好厭惡性既工作<br />\n我自己覺得 依家在職既護士人工同佢地既工作量，辛苦既程度絕對成正比<br />\nBro 哩個世界唔係下下都只係為錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba590bd7b0f16e43134200daa02ff00dd26ccb0e","tid":379850,"uid":141635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T16:35:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>IGCSE E or above</blockquote><br />\n Nursing council 承認？ 請問大大有無經驗or相關經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"894c18b92989415eb9eeaf146183443467c801f0","tid":379850,"uid":37874,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T16:36:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你讀nursing咪又係為錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實如果要搵錢的話 我大可以去做秘書 一勞永逸 人工又高<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但個人真心鐘情於醫護行業 唔識講 但我好鐘意關於人體 睇住自己照顧既病人康復走出醫院個種幫到人既感覺<br />\n護士人工係吸引，但相對都真係好厭惡性既工作<br />\n我自己覺得 依家在職既護士人工同佢地既工作量，辛苦既程度絕對成正比<br />\nBro 哩個世界唔係下下都只係為錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n&quot;其實如果要搵錢的話 我大可以去做秘書&quot;<br />\n細路女 出過黎社會做未 知唔知秘書做D咩同人工?<br />\n<br />\n定係你係想做有身材會著短裙低胸果D雞先咁講?"},{"pid":"62f6e85522e0ca2da4e6d0a5e961ea780885d915","tid":379850,"uid":60115,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T16:36:37.000Z","msg":"辣殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8722764333598944eee9440a95a7cccdebde0a40","tid":379850,"uid":8841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T16:39:02.000Z","msg":"retake + IGCSE + Asso<br />\n<br />\n身邊有朋友係咁，最後中文3到<br />\nIGCSE A* (呢個係弱智既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本用開中文字好難拎唔到A*)"},{"pid":"07740d3c1dcee77b089844d86bf806ae8d9cf221","tid":379850,"uid":141635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T16:40:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>IGCSE E or above</blockquote><br />\n Nursing council 承認？ 請問大大有無經驗or相關經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  大大有無經驗同相關information"},{"pid":"8620b6841f41979f0bb387971ce6a4f2215695be","tid":379850,"uid":30950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T16:41:41.000Z","msg":"一個月10k我幫你補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實中文要升4唔難，最緊要有心"},{"pid":"2bf2a853a546f1da0379b7f4cf6c0873c0eec983","tid":379850,"uid":141635,"like":1,"dislike":13,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T16:46:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你讀nursing咪又係為錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實如果要搵錢的話 我大可以去做秘書 一勞永逸 人工又高<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但個人真心鐘情於醫護行業 唔識講 但我好鐘意關於人體 睇住自己照顧既病人康復走出醫院個種幫到人既感覺<br />\n護士人工係吸引，但相對都真係好厭惡性既工作<br />\n我自己覺得 依家在職既護士人工同佢地既工作量，辛苦既程度絕對成正比<br />\nBro 哩個世界唔係下下都只係為錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n&quot;其實如果要搵錢的話 我大可以去做秘書&quot;<br />\n細路女 出過黎社會做未 知唔知秘書做D咩同人工?<br />\n<br />\n定係你係想做有身材會著短裙低胸果D雞先咁講?</blockquote><br />\n都做過幾年partime waitress 知道錢唔易搵 <br />\n但我以我所知秘書都係high pay 既行業<br />\n有個auntie 做秘書 2萬幾人工 做到覺得悶quit左<br />\n大大可以覺得我岩岩所講、如果要搵錢不如去做秘書 好似不諳世故 9up 串柒柒<br />\n但我只係想指出要搵錢唔一定係做護士"},{"pid":"8fd1a794c36bc86d09985b70f849b1f28cb3a6e9","tid":379850,"uid":141635,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T16:48:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>辣殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都成日笑柒自己 垃圾又要痴心妄想想讀Nursing<br />\n不過我不嬲在校成績都一向不差 2左中文真係意料之外"},{"pid":"dcca5278465e98fbc0b78cab6e0d5ded5111502b","tid":379850,"uid":141635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T16:50:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>retake + IGCSE + Asso<br />\n<br />\n身邊有朋友係咁，最後中文3到<br />\nIGCSE A* (呢個係弱智既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 根本用開中文字好難拎唔到A*)</blockquote><br />\n我連要讀邊幾篇範文都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都唔知從何入手 唉"},{"pid":"331da8fd3b90a2cb9a5497d326c7680e1fff18eb","tid":379850,"uid":48962,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T16:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831206585caae3ea1ce774704bf8ba278ad78aa4","tid":379850,"uid":141635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T16:59:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝大大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我都係retake 算啦"},{"pid":"240c1f1f6889014056098c110b0f73cfe5ba6463","tid":379850,"uid":64847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T17:04:08.000Z","msg":"一路讀asso 一路retake<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝你好運"},{"pid":"da51667f7ecad54c7528efd031b50cd72537de02","tid":379850,"uid":141635,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T17:07:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一路讀asso 一路retake<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n祝你好運</blockquote><br />\n我都覺得好2頭唔到岸 讀Asso就係唔想retake <br />\n結果自己on9 咁遲先見到3係必需<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548b19184143765fd077e972667c9b35850bcf67","tid":379850,"uid":47109,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T17:13:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你讀nursing咪又係為錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實如果要搵錢的話 我大可以去做秘書 一勞永逸 人工又高<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但個人真心鐘情於醫護行業 唔識講 但我好鐘意關於人體 睇住自己照顧既病人康復走出醫院個種幫到人既感覺<br />\n護士人工係吸引，但相對都真係好厭惡性既工作<br />\n我自己覺得 依家在職既護士人工同佢地既工作量，辛苦既程度絕對成正比<br />\nBro 哩個世界唔係下下都只係為錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n&quot;其實如果要搵錢的話 我大可以去做秘書&quot;<br />\n細路女 出過黎社會做未 知唔知秘書做D咩同人工?<br />\n<br />\n定係你係想做有身材會著短裙低胸果D雞先咁講?</blockquote><br />\n都做過幾年partime waitress 知道錢唔易搵 <br />\n但我以我所知秘書都係high pay 既行業<br />\n有個auntie 做秘書 2萬幾人工 做到覺得悶quit左<br />\n大大可以覺得我岩岩所講、如果要搵錢不如去做秘書 好似不諳世故 9up 串柒柒<br />\n但我只係想指出要搵錢唔一定係做護士</blockquote><br />\n2萬幾 做左幾多年  點解你會覺得係high pay"},{"pid":"14c0ff8b0c749c2a77e2c2599d8a13f33ab8efab","tid":379850,"uid":141643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T17:14:12.000Z","msg":"Cc health studies fm相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2863099a323b083cfed882e8ed2710c312894c82","tid":379850,"uid":55846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T17:16:55.000Z","msg":"我識人英文2左入東華 nursing HD, 升番上 degree 好似都得"},{"pid":"1795bb7063ce6f2e866ed7d11b88b01815c87846","tid":379850,"uid":141635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T17:18:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Cc health studies fm相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nHiiiii<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我到依家一個fm都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有d驚"},{"pid":"f1cfdc711b0f909464f32cf57efd00cc96f6268f","tid":379850,"uid":2986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08